fields.name: VeBNoR Men Regular Fit Printed Spread Collar Casual Shirt
fields.smDescription: This shirt boasts a modern yet classic design that seamlessly bridges the gap between casual.
fields.description:
Style That Speaks Volumes

This shirt boasts a modern yet classic design that seamlessly bridges the gap between casual and sophisticated. The regular fit ensures comfort without sacrificing style, making it suitable for a range of occasions, from casual Fridays at the office to weekend get-togethers. This design is tastefully incorporated to make a statement without overwhelming your outfit. Choose the print that best complements your personal style.

Spread Collar Sophistication

The spread collar, a hallmark of refined men's fashion, adds a dash of elegance to this shirt. It frames your face beautifully, making it suitable for both casual and semi-formal settings. Wear it with the top button open for a relaxed look, or button it up for a more polished appearance.

fields.name: VTEXX Men Regular Fit Solid Spread Collar Formal Shirt
fields.thumbnail_alt: VTEXX Men Regular Fit Solid Spread Collar Formal
fields.smDescription: A cornerstone of sophisticated attire, the VTEXX Mens Regular-fit Full-sleeve Formal Shirt.
fields.description:
Full Sleeves

A cornerstone of sophisticated attire, the VTEXX Men’s Regular-fit Full-sleeve Formal Shirt combines timeless style with functionality. Particularly suitable for professional settings and upscale occasions, this meticulously tailored formal shirt comes with full sleeves that offer refined aesthetics and provide added coverage and warmth. This long-sleeved shirt can seamlessly transition from formal to semi-formal with a simple rolling up of the sleeves. The contrasting border elevates the overall appeal while creating a relaxed yet stylish look.

Suitable for Various Occasions

Versatile and suitable for a wide range of body types, this regular-fit shirt can accommodate the natural contours of the body comfortably, allowing for ease of movement while creating a well-proportioned appearance. Exuding professionalism and attention to detail, this formal shirt can be worn to work or on occasions like business meetings, presentations, conferences, etc. You can style this solid shirt with a pair of dress pants or trousers or layer it with a well-fitted suit jacket or blazer for a classy, cohesive look.

fields.name: K' Footlance Running Shoes For Men  (Red)
fields.thumbnail_alt: K' Footlance Running Shoes For Men  (Red)
fields.smDescription: K' Footlance Running Shoes For Men
fields.description:
High-quality Material

The shoes have been crafted using premium materials to ensure durability and comfort. The inner part of the shoes has been crafted with cushion material while the exterior has been crafted from mesh. The sole is crafted from airmix material to ensure that the shoes maintain their durability for a long time.

Lace Closure

Featuring a lace closure, the shoes ensure a comfortable feeling while walking, running, or playing sports. You can tie the lace as per your own fit and make sure that the shoes are not loose or tight. This flexibility ensures that you do not feel tired even after a long time of walking, running, or indulging in sports.

fields.name: Bruton Lite Sports Shoes Running Shoes For Men  (Grey)
fields.smDescription: Providing you with the flexibility of adjusting the fit of the shoes as per your comfort and style.
fields.description:
Lace Closure for Flexibility

Providing you with the flexibility of adjusting the fit of the shoes as per your comfort and style, these shoes feature a lace closure. With the help of lace closure, you can easily tighten or loosen the fit of the shoes and make sure that there is enough flexibility of movement.

High-quality Upper Synthetic Leather

The shoes strike the ideal balance of style, durability, and comfort as the upper part of the shoes has been constructed from synthetic leather. The use of premium synthetic leather makes sure that the shoes do not lose their quality and comfort for a long time. Additionally, the synthetic leather material also gives the shoes a glossy look that adds to their style quotient.
